            "title": "Delta Earnings Take Off on Travel Rebound",
            "description": "<div class=\"txt-s4 article-text\"><div class=\"akcelo-wrapper akcelo-video media--169\" style=\"width:100%\"><div class=\"border:solid 1px #C0C0C0\" id=\"Zonebourse_Article_Video\" video-id=\"kc1EO1zzvSchUSE013A\"><div itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"https://schema.org/VideoObject\"><meta content=\"Delta Earnings Take Off on Travel Rebound\" itemprop=\"name\"/><meta content=\"On the earnings front Delta delivers a stronger-than-expected third quarter, boosted by resilient leisure demand and a rebound in business travel. TD Cowen's Tom Fitzgerald joined Bloomberg Open Interest to talk about the carrier's tailwinds and the outlook for the air travel industry during the government shutdown.\n\" itemprop=\"description\"/><meta content=\"2025-10-09T17:04:59+02:00\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/><meta content=\"/images/mtnewswires/A3473714.png\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/><meta content=\"https://geo.dailymotion.com/player/x80uo.html?video=kc1EO1zzvSchUSE013A\" itemprop=\"embedUrl\"/></div></div></div>\n               On the earnings front Delta delivers a stronger-than-expected third quarter, boosted by resilient leisure demand and a rebound in business travel. TD Cowen's Tom Fitzgerald joined Bloomberg Open Interest to talk about the carrier's tailwinds and the outlook for the air travel industry during the government shutdown.<p><span class=\"js-l-obf link link--blue\" data-lobf=\"v4fox4ar=NTQyQxJmBMKwpP7nl8C=BbKwgTpvkfAwLuu\" data-tobf=\"blank\" onclick=\"gaEvent('Out', 'mtnewswires', '51301389');\">Bloomberg videos</span>, provided by MT Newswires</p></div>",
